title: Ep 382 - Water Conservation
shortDesc: Bhide informs all the women in the society that the water supply has been cut in half and that they will have to start saving water. All the women agree to be more careful while using water.

title: Ep 383 - Water Problem Because Of Sodhi
shortDesc: Everyone is wondering why there's no water in the society. Just then, Sodhi arrives and says that he doesn't remember turning the tap off. Did Sodhi cause the water problem in the society?

title: Ep 384 - Gadas Have Too Many Visitors
shortDesc: The Gadas have a few visitors early in the morning. When Jethalal gives Sundar permission to take bath, he assumes there are two people. But, to his surprise, Sundar brings his entire family. Jethalal is worried about creating a water issue again.

title: Ep 385 - The Water War
shortDesc: One of Daya's guests creates a scene and starts a fight with Bhide and other society members. The water issue now has crossed the line. How will the society find a solution to this?

title: Ep 386 - Gadas Facing Trouble
shortDesc: Now that the Gadas have guests home, they're facing troubles with cleanliness. Jethalal finds gutkha packets in his room and a few stains on the bed sheets. How will Jethalal deal with this problem along with the water problem?

title: Ep 387 - Daya Makes Difficulties Fun
shortDesc: Now that the water tanker is arriving, everyone at Gokuldham is waiting for the water. But, Daya is excited to fill water in their buckets. How will the water problem get solved?

title: Ep 388 - Popatlal The Water Thief
shortDesc: While Jethalal gets water for Babita, Popatlal slyly exchanges his buckets and takes the bucket with water. When Jethalal finds out, he gets into an argument with him. What will happen next? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 389 - Taarak Plans to Write An Article On Children
shortDesc: Taarak plans to write an article about children and their parents' tension after vacation. He plans to write an article about getting back to school and vacations.

title: Ep 390 - Its GPL Time
shortDesc: It is time for Gokuldham Premier League. But, Bhide announces that there will be no GPL as the society has fewer funds. How will Tappu Sena react? How will Sundar's call help these kids in arranging GPL? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep. 391 - Jethalal Against Gokuldam Premier League - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethala is worried about Sundar taking initiatives to conduct the Gokuldam Premier League 2. But Nattu on another hand is so much excited about the match and plans to advertise their company without informing Jethala.

title: Ep. 392 - Pre Plans For GPL 2 - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sundar calls in for two chief guests who play as the captain for the two teams playing in the Gokulam Premier league. But turns out be team spirit didn't stop in the grounds, rather got into the Jethala and Daya who stands opposing each other for the

title: Ep. 393 - Gokuldham Team's Rigorous Training - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita's and Daya's team gets ready for the GPL 2 and they start practicing for the match. While Babita's team finds a military coach who puts them in rigorous Training and the other teams goes casual. The team spirit lightens up between them.

title: Ep. 394 - Long Awaited Moment Arrives - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The Gokuldam Premier League begins, the ground is set ready and teams are ready to compete. As this is going to go live on the shows, the teams are excited. On another hand, the rigorous training made Babita's team tired.

title: Ep. 395 - Blaster Babita Versus Daya Dandiya Devil - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Fun-filled Gokuldam Premier league 2 begins, Hence the match begins with the coin toss, though Daya team wins the toss; She chose Feilding. Hence Taarak enters the field as the opening batsman, but eventually, he fails and Jethala enters the field.

title: Ep. 396 - Fun Packed GPL Match - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The Gokuldam premier league 2 is filled with team spirit. Babita's and Daya team are putting up their best to win the match, they enjoy while they play and make mistakes.
